<lb ed="X" n="0924c19"/><lb ed="R101" n="0170b01"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0924c1901"><l>澄江杳杳映千峰</l><l>坐夏巖房一望中</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0924c20"/><lb ed="R101" n="0170b02"/><l>晝講疎鐘清度越</l><l>夜吟殘月冷垂空</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0924c21"/><lb ed="R101" n="0170b03"/><l>埽軒靜避堦稜蘚</l><l>銷暑閑當竹罅風</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0924c22"/><lb ed="R101" n="0170b04"/><l>顧我相懷未能去</l><l>水邊斜日照梧桐</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0924c23"/><lb ed="R101" n="0170b05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">寄遠</cb:mulu><head>寄遠</head>
